Republican leaders struggle to find v... Republican leaders struggle to find votes to up debt limit There are 1 comment on the Fox News story from 8 hrs ago, titled Republican leaders struggle to find votes to up debt limit . In it, Fox News reports that: 
Congressional Republicans say they are short of the votes for raising the debt limit and avoiding a first-ever government default. With barely a week before deadline, there's no plan on what to do. Join the discussion below, or Read more at Fox News.
